     F************************************ ABBR18 **
     FABBWP18 IP  F      70            DISK
     FABBNP17 O   E                    DISK
     E                    N1         31  7 0             N-1日当実績数
     IABBWP18 AA  01
     I                                       34  45 ASHIN L1
     I                                       46  520ASURY
     I                                       62  690ANOHZ
     I                                       62  670ANOYM
     I                                       68  690ANODD
